org.apache.hadoop.hive.llap.daemon.impl

Class LlapTaskReporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.llap.daemon.impl.LlapTaskReporter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.tez.runtime.internals.api.TaskReporterInterface

    public class LlapTaskReporter
extends Object
implements org.apache.tez.runtime.internals.api.TaskReporterInterface
    Responsible for communication between tasks running in a Container and the ApplicationMaster. Takes care of sending heartbeats (regular and OOB) to the AM - to send generated events, and to retrieve events specific to this task.
